OL,6,FThe firm said the morning data jumps
OL,7,Fhad emerged as part of its broadband
OL,8,Fnetwork analysis, which it said was a
OL,9,Freliable indicator of the connectivity
OL,10,Fhabits of the British public.
OL,12,FIt found three jumps ` evident almost
OL,13,Fimmediately following the hours of
OL,14,F6am, 7am and 8am ` suggesting people
OL,15,Freach for their phones to turn off
OL,16,Ftheir alarms and immediately begin
OL,17,Fscrolling.
