OL,6,FSome 81% of Britons said they reached
OL,7,Ffor their phones first thing most
OL,8,Fdays, with 75% immediately checking
OL,9,Ftheir social media feeds and more than
OL,10,Fhalf (52%) checking news feeds.
OL,12,FA fifth (21%) said they looked at the
OL,13,Fday's forecast, while 18% checked for
OL,14,Fdisruptions to their commute.
OL,16,FSome 6% scanned the stock market
OL,17,Fbefore they got out of bed.
